WEBVTT

00:16.058 --> 00:17.893
Gorbash...

00:18.101 --> 00:19.560
Gorbash...

00:20.062 --> 00:21.021
Come!

00:38.664 --> 00:41.833
<i>Man: There was a time between
the waning age of enchantment</i>

00:42.042 --> 00:46.542
<i>and the dawning age of logic
when dragons flew the skies</i>

00:47.256 --> 00:49.091
<i>free and unencumbered.</i>

01:01.895 --> 01:04.647
Look down there,
gorbash, my friend.

01:04.897 --> 01:06.357
On that troubled earth
below us,

01:06.567 --> 01:08.986
confusion and chaos reign.

01:09.194 --> 01:12.238
All mankind is facing
an epic choice --

01:12.489 --> 01:15.950
a world of magic
or a world of science.

01:16.535 --> 01:18.411
Which will it be?

01:19.705 --> 01:22.958
H' flight of dragons <i>h'</i>

01:23.625 --> 01:28.125
h' soar in the purple light <i>h'</i>

01:28.797 --> 01:32.133
h' in the sky <i>h'</i>

01:33.218 --> 01:37.639
h' or in my mind <i>h'</i>

01:37.848 --> 01:41.518
h' flight of dragons <i>h'</i>

01:41.893 --> 01:46.393
h' sail past reality <i>h'</i>

01:47.190 --> 01:51.690
h' leave illusion behind h'

01:55.741 --> 02:00.241
h' is it the past I see <i>h'</i>

02:01.455 --> 02:05.955
<i>h'</i> when I look up
to the heavens h'

02:06.460 --> 02:10.422
h' believing in the magic <i>h'</i>

02:10.631 --> 02:14.009
h' that I know could never be? H'

02:14.217 --> 02:18.717
<i>n'</i> I want to go
where they are going <i>h'</i>

02:20.223 --> 02:24.352
h' into the world they've been <i>h'</i>

02:24.561 --> 02:29.061
n' can I open up
my mind enough to see? <i>H'</i>

02:32.944 --> 02:36.572
h' flight of dragons <i>h'</i>

02:37.115 --> 02:41.577
h' heavenly argosies h'

02:42.329 --> 02:45.790
h' catch the wind <i>h'</i>

02:46.208 --> 02:50.708
h' rise out of sight <i>h'</i>

02:51.254 --> 02:55.132
h' flight of dragons <i>h'</i>

02:55.384 --> 02:59.884
h' pilots of fantasy <i>h'</i>

03:00.430 --> 03:04.183
h' in the sky <i>h'</i>

03:04.393 --> 03:08.772
h' or in my mind <i>h'</i>

03:09.481 --> 03:13.610
h' flight of dragons <i>h'</i>

03:14.111 --> 03:18.611
h' flight of dragons <i>h'</i>

03:33.714 --> 03:34.589
